{"tid":81520,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"下個月去巴塞隆拿 求介紹","createTime":"2017-01-15T11:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T06:56:54.000Z","uid":14799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5319464d52b7882781d3e74afc68c024637a4e99","tid":81520,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"我下個月去巴賽經巴黎轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目前暴想去只有魯營<br />\n有無巴打介紹下有乜必食必玩必睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dbb13a8503dc090addb7977f845d36fd03a7fd","tid":81520,"uid":64443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"食：Mercado de La Boqueria<br />\n依個market一定要去 好多地道野食<br />\n2年前去Barcelona朝朝早餐都係果到搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMetro Liceu 果條街同埋Plaza real都有好多餐廳<br />\n不過主要做遊客生意 所以要睇多幾間同睇下menu先<br />\n<br />\n玩：去海邊搭吊車上山 可以睇曬Barcelona全海灘<br />\n<br />\nLa Sagrada Familia 就一定要去啦 唔洗多講"},{"pid":"f11f84f499f39f14dca6ca90de1bc610ccc1f225","tid":81520,"uid":54171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"聖家堂記得上網買左tix先"},{"pid":"de861016fbe1dbed8f68fb797e5adf8c2c6a55fb","tid":81520,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T18:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食：Mercado de La Boqueria<br />\n依個market一定要去 好多地道野食<br />\n2年前去Barcelona朝朝早餐都係果到搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMetro Liceu 果條街同埋Plaza real都有好多餐廳<br />\n不過主要做遊客生意 所以要睇多幾間同睇下menu先<br />\n<br />\n玩：去海邊搭吊車上山 可以睇曬Barcelona全海灘<br />\n<br />\nLa Sagrada Familia 就一定要去啦 唔洗多講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx"},{"pid":"430e6aef8364486003a293b416786933b4a20174","tid":81520,"uid":32769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:08:40.000Z","msg":"主要景點一定要一早買定飛，唔係排隊排到你傻<br />\n<br />\n上次去好似casa Mila , Sagrada Familia 好在上網買左飛，見到排隊買飛人龍圍住個景點排左一個圈"},{"pid":"bc780b1b07ab80cd67486a59240d0b012637065e","tid":81520,"uid":22270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"食左西班牙海鮮飯 聖家堂 同魯營<br />\n但係魯營入唔到去入面<br />\n淨係得紀念品商店入到屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017d336858b0c79b11cf14683fba44e7e9621130","tid":81520,"uid":54171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左西班牙海鮮飯 聖家堂 同魯營<br />\n但係魯營入唔到去入面<br />\n淨係得紀念品商店入到屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買波飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，對d 垃圾隊好平。大把位，我果次睇山頂幾碼有1/3 空的。果場對畢爾包，早幾個月官網入手，好似仲大炒。不過我反巴的，入敵陣了解下"},{"pid":"64e861b30a52d3fc447a45c1f210dbac69f385a1","tid":81520,"uid":68192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"睇 antonio gaudi啲博物館 仲有 畢加索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇波 話說我睇咗巴主場對鏝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坐bus tour都唔錯"},{"pid":"839210ec44272d8d5fed0a19581c6e410f404792","tid":81520,"uid":3175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左西班牙海鮮飯 聖家堂 同魯營<br />\n但係魯營入唔到去入面<br />\n淨係得紀念品商店入到屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/230727_f82dbb24fedf9ca18cb83df7a1043956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F230727_f82dbb24fedf9ca18cb83df7a1043956.jpg&h=f365ac49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRSFr56RiX4XauyXRiJbrtv26f1Sr9MrMgoWkdpPrc9db?filename=W431KR1.jpg\" data-thumbn